snippet.title: The Good People (Na Daoine Maithe) | Footage Trailer 2024
snippet.description:
The new demo drops tomorrow! Are you excited? Wishlist on Steam and follow on Itch.io! 

☆ STEAM: http://bit.ly/3Jl3bO6
☆ ITCH: http://bit.ly/3SemOLK
☆ PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/moiraimyths
☆ ALL ELSE: https://moiraimyths.com/links

˗ˏˋ ★ ˎˊ˗

The Good People (Na Daoine Maithe) is a lore-rich, choice-driven visual novel inspired by Irish myths and developed by Moirai Myths. Venture into Tír na nÓg, the Celtic Otherworld, in order to retrieve your family's stolen valuables...and get swept up in deadly fairy politics and a whirlwind romance along the way.

˗ˏˋ ★ ˎˊ˗

Music: Adventure by Alexander Nakarada (www.creatorchords.com)
